import pic6 from '../assets/svg/projects/six.svg'
import pic4 from '../assets/svg/projects/four.svg'
import pic3 from '../assets/svg/projects/three.svg'
import pic5 from '../assets/svg/projects/five.svg'
import pic2 from '../assets/svg/projects/two.svg'
import pic1 from '../assets/svg/projects/one.svg'


export const projectsData = [
    {
        id: 1,
        projectName: 'Full Stack Blogging App',
        projectDesc: 'Using this app, users can write blogs and can blogs of other writers too.',
        tags: ['React', 'CSS', 'NodeJS', 'Javascript', 'MongoDB'],
        code: 'https://github.com/shubham-20120/full-stack-blog-app',
        image: pic5
    },
    {
        id: 2,
        projectName: 'P-Foodies',
        projectDesc: 'Using this project, users can search for the food reciepes according to ingredients they want.',
        tags: ['React', 'Javascript', 'HTML', 'CSS'],
        code: 'https://github.com/shubham-20120/p-foodies',
        image: pic3
    },
    {
        id: 3,
        projectName: 'Gy-Monitor',
        projectDesc: 'Using this project, user can count reps in their Gym excercise automatically',
        tags: ['Deep Learning', 'Python', 'Convolution Neural Networks', 'OpenCV'],
        code: 'https://github.com/shubham-20120/GyMonitor',
        image: pic5
    },
    {
        id: 4,
        projectName: 'Quiz App',
        projectDesc: 'using this app, user can create Quiz/online tests for various purposes',
        tags: ['React', 'Javascript', 'HTML', 'CSS'],
        code: 'https://github.com/shubham-20120/quiz-app-ReactJS',
        image: pic4
    },
    {
        id: 5,
        projectName: 'Youtube Clone',
        projectDesc: 'This is the cloning of Youtube Android Mobile app',
        tags: ['React Native', 'JavaScript'],
        code: 'https://github.com/shubham-20120/youtube-clone-react-native',
        image: pic1
    },
    {
        id: 6,
        projectName: 'Finance tracker',
        projectDesc: 'Using this project, users can track their income and expenses very easily.',
        tags: ['React Native', 'JavaScript', 'NodeJS', 'MongoDB', 'ExpressJS'],
        code: 'https://github.com/shubham-20120/finance-tracking-mobile-app',
        image: pic3
    },
    {
        id: 7,
        projectName: 'Crypto Price Prediction',
        projectDesc: 'This is the Machine Learning model that predicts future price of Crypto, this can be extended to stock market also.',
        tags: ['Python', 'Machine Learning', 'LSTM', 'Numpy', 'Pandas'],
        code: 'https://github.com/shubham-20120/crypto_price_prediction',
        image: pic2
    },
    {
        id: 8,
        projectName: 'bookmark browser extension',
        projectDesc: 'This is the browser extension that allows user to bookmark and manage any website using shortcuts',
        tags: ['Javascript', 'HTML', 'CSS'],
        code: 'https://github.com/shubham-20120/chrome-bookmark-extension',
        image: pic6
    },
    {
        id: 9,
        projectName: 'Customer Churn Prediction',
        projectDesc: 'This is ML model that predict whether customer will buy premium services or not based on their past interaction with the system',
        tags: ['Machine Learning', 'Python', 'Numpy', 'Pandas'],
        code: 'https://github.com/shubham-20120/customer-churn-prediction-using-ML',
        image: pic5
    },
]
